#Set up Component and folder structure.

##What functionalities does a shopping cart need?
+ first be able to show the products you chose
+ keep the looks even if the user chooses other links to products.
+ increase the amount of objects
+ remove the products
+ either show up from the left side or show it as a popup

##How to structure the folder?
Create a component folder for each component if they are big, else keep it cool
